text: Andrei Kerekeş (9 January 1925 - 3 January 1991) was a Romanian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1925 births Category:1991 deaths Category:Romanian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Romania Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Reșița
